    </arrangement>
    <scopecontent id="aspace_hzc210880n520as03449724075174">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>The papers of Thom Sudato measure 0.2 linear feet, date from 1972-1976, and provide scattered documentation of Sudato's career through correspondence, poems, photographs of Sudato, his wife Gina Sudato, and his artwork, and documentation of paintings he gave to Gina Sudato.</p>
    </scopecontent>
